<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EvidenceBench</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #F8F9FF;
        }

        .navbar {
            box-shadow: 0 2px 2px -2px gray;
            background-color: white !important;
            height: 70px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .expandable-div {
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .expandable-div .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .expandable-div .content {
            display: none;
            padding-top: 10px;
        }
      
        .floating-div {
          background-color: #f8f9fa; 
          border: 1px solid #ddd;
          border-radius: 8px;
          padding: 20px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
          transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .floating-div .links {
          margin-top: 15px;
      }

      .floating-div .btn {
          margin-right: 10px;
      }
      
      .floating-div .links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .floating-div .btn {
        margin: 0 5px;
    }



    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">EvidenceBench</a>
    </nav>


   
    <div class="container mt-4">
       
       <div class="floating-div" id="description-div">
    <h4>About EvidenceBench</h4>
    <p>Longer description about the mission, reasons, background, abstract etc. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam tincidunt, nisl eget vestibulum rhoncus, elit neque euismod orci, eu vulputate leo magna id erat. Curabitur et diam vel ligula malesuada vehicula. Praesent auctor purus nec ipsum pulvinar, a venenatis libero egestas.</p>
    <div class="links">
        <a target="_blank" href="https://example.com/" class="btn btn-dark">Paper</a>
        <a target="_blank" href="https://example.com/" class="btn btn-dark">Lab Group</a>
        <a target="_blank" href="https://example.com/" class="btn btn-dark">GitHub</a>
    </div>
</div>
       
        <div class="expandable-div" id="div-1">
            <div class="header">
                <h5>Description of Benchmark</h5>
                <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="toggleContent(1)" id="button-1">+</button>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Here we would include the description of the benchmark and all relevant details.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="expandable-div" id="div-2">
            <div class="header">
                <h5>Evaluation Metrics</h5>
                <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="toggleContent(2)" id="button-2">+</button>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Here we would provide an explanation for the evaluation metrics, etc.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="expandable-div" id="div-3">
            <div class="header">
                <h5>Example/Case Study</h5>
                <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="toggleContent(3)" id="button-3">+</button>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>An example/case study could go here. We could also put it on a different page if needed.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="expandable-div" id="div-4">
            <div class="header">
                <h5>Model Leaderboard</h5>
                <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="toggleContent(4)" id="button-4">+</button>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>A leaderboard for the models could go here. Again, this could be moved to its own page if needed.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="expandable-div" id="div-5">
            <div class="header">
                <h5>Other</h5>
                <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="toggleContent(5)" id="button-5">+</button>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Any other aspects could be added.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function toggleContent(id) {
            const content = document.querySelector(`#div-${id} .content`);
            const button = document.querySelector(`#button-${id}`);
            if (content.style.display === "none" || content.style.display === "") {
                content.style.display = "block";
                button.textContent = "-";
            } else {
                content.style.display = "none";
                button.textContent = "+";
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
